{"tid":230564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅十字會出席五四運動升旗禮","createTime":"2017-05-05T12:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T10:37:35.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d2cd39f55e563ae6b1e3b9abb397a31f77c5cf5","tid":230564,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"讀五四宣言 自強振興中華<br />\n<br />\n【香港商報訊】記者馮仁樂報道：昨日是五四運動98周年，香港各界青少年活動委員會早上8時正在灣仔金紫荊廣場舉行升旗禮。由本港14個青少年制服團體<span style=\"color: red;\">包括紅十字會</span>、航空青年團等負責儀仗和步操，各團體代表最后與來賓站立於國旗與區旗下，共同宣讀《五四宣言》。主辦單位指出，<span style=\"color: blue;\">希望透過升旗禮讓香港青少年回顧「五四」運動歷史，使他們認識前人為振興民族、國家富強而矢志奮斗的事迹</span>，從而進一步加強青年人的團結精神。"},{"pid":"3fd754fbcc784f49a5d9465a1ae08bd7fe3575b9","tid":230564,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:54:03.000Z","msg":"紅十字？其實係咪同大陸個同一個會來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6292055ed7da433d3f8edaf6267f504d036547","tid":230564,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:55:19.000Z","msg":"捐血震興支那人？不了😴"},{"pid":"207e3f0889a52b3fed777ff3f528ee579e14c18c","tid":230564,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:02:55.000Z","msg":"郭美美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7240d6f52d574130a631d7a2bf6ebd597c8eef4","tid":230564,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:53:43.000Z","msg":"正名「支那紅十字會香港分會」<br />\n<br />\n要香港人記住佢地係支那會"},{"pid":"b1b6eb239a81d09039b93e76bbca10fd64949c2a","tid":230564,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:54:26.000Z","msg":"五四運動？<br />\n<br />\n放火打柒D狗官？"},{"pid":"8f35ed6254cd928a1edd59f98d1c126362178814","tid":230564,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:03:01.000Z","msg":"終於都支那化"},{"pid":"079d52a7eb2841b5e728a3ae44df32febba5fc9f","tid":230564,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"